Package: reUnderwriteR
Title: Reinsurance Underwriting Toolkit with CAS Portfolio, Treaty Simulation, API and Shiny Frontend
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Marco", "Ramljak", , "marcoramljak@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A minimal prototype demonstrating a modern reinsurance underwriting workflow: 
    loading and preparing a motor insurance portfolio based on CASdatasets, computing 
    portfolio KPIs, evaluating a simple quota share treaty structure.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    plumber,
    jsonlite,
    CASdatasets,
    ellmer
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.1.0),
    ggplot2,
    shiny,
    rmarkdown,
    knitr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
